Install all the prerequisites of the MetaCPAN Web front-end
https://github.com/CPAN-API/metacpan-web

Normally you should go with the instructions provided by the MetaCPAN authors
and use the cpanfile included in the https://github.com/CPAN-API/metacpan-web
but some people might like to live on the bleeding edge.

The cpanfile included in this distribution should be a copy of the file
located in https://github.com/CPAN-API/metacpan-web

